Key Match Events: Khalil Khamsi's header from Kassem El Zein’s throw-in was saved by Yan Junling.
Omar Chaban’s right-footed attempt hit the side netting.
Dai Weijun forced Mostafa Matar into action with two attempts.
Hasan Matouk’s right-footed shot was denied by the crossbar.
Zhang Linpeng’s header from the centre of the box was parried away.
Hasan Srour’s right-footed shot was fisted away by Junling.
Maher Sabra’s header was cleared by Junling.
Wu Lei’s shot from inside the six-yard box was denied by Srour.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Al Thumama Stadium in Doha.
Both teams needed victory to progress to the Round of 16.
